WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.735 --> 00:00:03.203
[rapping gavel]

00:00:03.237 --> 00:00:04.805
- DR. ARMOND, PLEASE RISE.

00:00:04.838 --> 00:00:08.108
YOU STAND HERE ACCUSED OF MURDER
IN THE SECOND DEGREE.

00:00:08.141 --> 00:00:09.543
HOW DO YOU PLEAD?

00:00:09.576 --> 00:00:11.778
- GUILTY...OF LOVING MY WIFE.

00:00:11.812 --> 00:00:13.514
- [laughs]

00:00:13.547 --> 00:00:15.482
- HMM, WELL,
WE'LL SEE ABOUT THAT.

00:00:15.516 --> 00:00:16.617
I THINK THE COURT WILL DECIDE

00:00:16.650 --> 00:00:19.686
THAT PROBABLY
YOU'RE GUILTY OF MURDER.

00:00:19.720 --> 00:00:21.321
[hawk screeches]

00:00:21.355 --> 00:00:23.123
[intense music]

00:00:23.156 --> 00:00:25.325 line:0%
 
- OPENING ARGUMENTS
WERE AN ABSOLUTE SLAUGHTER

00:00:25.359 --> 00:00:27.594 line:0%
 
AS FRIENDLY
DEFENSE ATTORNEY RON FUNCHES

00:00:27.628 --> 00:00:29.463 line:0%
 
COULDN'T COPE WITH THE ONSLAUGHT

00:00:29.496 --> 00:00:32.766 line:0%
 
FROM HARD-CHARGING PROSECUTOR
RUTH DIAMOND PHILLIPS.

00:00:32.799 --> 00:00:34.434 line:0%
 
- A LOT CAN HAPPEN
IN TEN SECONDS.

00:00:34.468 --> 00:00:36.003 line:0%
 
YOU'D BE SURPRISED.

00:00:36.036 --> 00:00:38.272 line:0%
 
LET ME SURPRISE YOU.

00:00:38.305 --> 00:00:40.874 line:0%
 
ONE, HE BUSTS INTO THE ROOM.

00:00:40.908 --> 00:00:42.543 line:0%
 
TWO, "SHUT UP,"
HE PROBABLY SAID.

00:00:42.576 --> 00:00:43.777 line:0%
 
WHO KNOWS?

00:00:43.810 --> 00:00:46.713 line:0%
 
THREE, HE TAKES OUT
A LARGE NEEDLE

00:00:46.747 --> 00:00:50.851 line:0%
 
TO PUT DOWN HORSES
THAT HAVE HURT THEIR FEET

00:00:50.884 --> 00:00:53.820 line:0%
 
BECAUSE THEY RUN TOO FAST
IN RACES

00:00:53.854 --> 00:00:56.023 line:0%
 
AND ACTUALLY,
THEY CAN'T EVEN LIVE ANYMORE

00:00:56.056 --> 00:00:57.858 line:0%
 
AND THEY HAVE TO
PUT THEM DOWN.

00:00:57.891 --> 00:01:01.261 line:0%
 
HE PUTS THE NEEDLE
INTO HER FOREHEAD,

00:01:01.295 --> 00:01:03.230 line:0%
 
THROWS HER ACROSS THE ROOM

00:01:03.263 --> 00:01:07.467 line:0%
 
WITH THE BRUTE STRENGTH
OF A VETERINARIAN.

00:01:07.501 --> 00:01:09.870 line:0%
 
- WHILE RON FUNCHES
SEEMS TO BE PLAYING A GAME,

00:01:09.903 --> 00:01:11.805 line:0%
 
THE RULES OF WHICH
WE DO NOT KNOW.

00:01:11.839 --> 00:01:16.610 line:0%
 
- WOULD A MURDERER
WEAR THAT HILARIOUS APRON?

00:01:16.643 --> 00:01:18.545 line:0%
 
[snickering]

00:01:18.579 --> 00:01:20.981 line:0%
 
LOOK AT THAT APRON.

00:01:21.081 --> 00:01:23.116 line:0%
 
- AS FOR THE WITNESSES,
DETECTIVE SMART'S TESTIMONY

00:01:23.150 --> 00:01:24.918 line:0%
 
SHOULD'VE BEEN ENOUGH
TO CONVINCE ANYONE.

00:01:24.952 --> 00:01:26.286 line:0%
 
THE FORENSICS WERE DAZZLING.

00:01:26.320 --> 00:01:27.788 line:0%
 
- AT THAT POINT,
I WOULD IMAGINE

00:01:27.821 --> 00:01:30.090 line:0%
 
THAT HIS TORSO WAS RIGHT UP
AGAINST THAT--

00:01:30.090 --> 00:01:31.959 line:0%
 
THAT HEAVING BOSOM.
- MM.

00:01:31.992 --> 00:01:34.628 line:0%
 
- I'M SURPRISED HE WAS ABLE TO
GET THE SYRINGE KIND OF PAST...

00:01:34.661 --> 00:01:37.097 line:0%
 
- PAST JUST HOW THE BREASTS
WOULD PROBABLY

00:01:37.097 --> 00:01:39.967 line:0%
 
ALMOST STAND AT ATTENTION.

00:01:40.000 --> 00:01:41.568 line:0%
 
- LIKE, UH...

00:01:41.602 --> 00:01:43.203 line:0%
 
DOMINIQUE WILKINS
BACK IN THE DAY,

00:01:43.237 --> 00:01:44.838 line:0%
 
THAT TOMAHAWK SLAM
HE USED TO DO?

00:01:44.872 --> 00:01:46.673 line:0%
 
- YEAH.
- YEAH, SO PUT LIKE A SYRINGE

00:01:46.707 --> 00:01:49.109 line:0%
 
RIGHT THROUGH HER FOREHEAD.
- THE HUMAN HIGHLIGHT FILM.

00:01:50.777 --> 00:01:52.112 line:0%
 
- THAT IS TRUE.

00:01:52.112 --> 00:01:54.715 line:0%
 
- EVEN HIS OWN SON COULDN'T SAY
HE DIDN'T DO IT.

00:01:54.748 --> 00:01:56.316 line:0%
 
- YOU'RE NOT COOL AT ALL.

00:01:56.350 --> 00:01:58.952 line:0%
 
YOU'RE COMPLETELY
THE OPPOSITE OF COOL.

00:01:58.986 --> 00:02:02.556 line:0%
 
- HE'S THE OPPOSITE OF COOL.
- YUP.

00:02:02.589 --> 00:02:06.326 line:0%
 
- MIGHT THAT BE...
A MURDERER?

00:02:06.360 --> 00:02:07.961 line:0%
 
- YEAH.
[courtroom murmuring]

00:02:08.061 --> 00:02:08.962 line:0%
 
- GO GET 'EM, RUTH.

00:02:09.062 --> 00:02:12.065 line:0%
 
[intense music]

